# Static analysis — finish checklist

## When to run

After TypeScript, HTML, or style changes. Skip docs-only / `.mdc`-only edits.

## Required commands (match CI)

```bash
npm ci
npm test -- --watch=false --browsers=ChromeHeadless
npm run build -- --configuration=production
```

## IDE diagnostics

`ReadLints` on changed files; fix new TypeScript and template errors.

## Do not finish while

- `npm run build` fails.
- Tests fail on your branch.
- New linter errors in touched files.

## Report to the user

Briefly note: build (pass/fail), tests (pass/fail), linter (clean/fixed).
